REQUIRED LIBRARIES
------------------
tabulate

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To run unit tests from Adminstrator/

pytest unit-test.py


To run the Game between Automated Players from Adminstrator/

python3 AutomatedGamePlay.py

On running the above command, you will see a prompt like :

Pick a strategy for the player, 1 -> Ordered, 2 -> Random ----> 

Enter 1 to pick Ordered strategy for the player
Enter 2 to pick Random strategy for player

A sample game output with both players playing with ordered strategy is in the Adminstrator/sample_output.txt file (both players use ordered strategy)

 

